{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/1280_720_grim.png?t=1737119825\" />  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What Awaits You in the Grimstone Survivors Demo?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grimstone Survivors is a 3D roguelite offering endless playability! The demo will consist of 10-15 levels, and we will continue development with your feedback. New updates are on the way! If you enjoy our game, feel free to join our Discord channel and share your thoughts. And don't forget to add it to your wishlist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">3D Top-Down Roguelite Experience:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Breathe new life into the roguelite genre with 3D top-down shooter depth. Experience action-packed battles in an adventure where death is not the end and every new beginning makes you stronger.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/ezgif-7-c71a62d64d.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic Weapon Combinations:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Shape the battlefield to your playstyle by carrying different weapons in each hand. Hunt enemies from afar with a long-range weapon, while preparing for sudden attacks with a melee weapon in your other hand. Each weapon combination offers a different strategic advantage, discover the deadliest combination!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/ezgif-7-57151a7049__1_.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Personalized Skill Tree:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from a wide variety of abilities to create your own unique playstyle. Whether you're increasing your stamina as a life-stealing specialist or taking down enemies with fast attacks, each skill selection will make you unique.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/market1.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic and Surprising Battlefield:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Momentary events can turn the tide of battle in an instant. Gain a tactical advantage over your enemies by launching turrets or life towers. Using the battlefield wisely is key to survival.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/ezgif-6-459c45c7bd.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic Resource Management:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The Market offers you different paths. Get instant advantages by buying temporary power-ups from the market. Managing your resources wisely will help you survive challenging levels.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Add to Your Wishlist:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can support us by adding our game to your wishlist during the development process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Blood","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3270630/6b5ff3a852a4d94d535d07af1a2a86956c83574e.jpg"},{"name":"Level Up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3270630/ed1bf9899b63d61126d3e550e00ae3b224f54e18.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3270630/a4182afdb172d66daceff80ffe645e3239402413.jpg"},{"name":"e-Roller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3270630/4681d86c21b22778393675539fb013c06330b60c.jpg"},{"name":"Shopper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity