ife-stealing specialist or taking down enemies with fast attacks, each skill selection will make you unique.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/market1.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic and Surprising Battlefield:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Momentary events can turn the tide of battle in an instant. Gain a tactical advantage over your enemies by launching turrets or life towers. Using the battlefield wisely is key to survival.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/extras/ezgif-6-459c45c7bd.gif?t=1737119825\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic Resource Management:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The Market offers you different paths. Get instant advantages by buying temporary power-ups from the market. Managing your resources wisely will help you survive challenging levels.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Add to Your Wishlist:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can support us by adding our game to your wishlist during the development process. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","developers":["Red Axe Games"],"fullgame":{"appid":"3158620","name":"Grimstone Survivors"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270630/header.jpg?t=1737119825","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":false,"id":257061029,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061029/movie480.mp4?t=1728420814","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061029/movie_max.mp4?t